dialogueList.name: Coco
dialogueList.text: Hey Player,its Coco, glad to see you back on the track, its been a long time coming.

dialogueList.name: Coco
dialogueList.text: YES! , I can't wait for this. Hope you've got your best engine in.

dialogueList.name: NARRATOR
dialogueList.text: This is the Advanced racetrack, this is where you relly test your skills as a Hoverdriver, race to the end and finish in first place.

dialogueList.name: NARRATOR
dialogueList.text: Use WASD to move. Good luck driver.
